msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/first-steps/ad-hoc-shell-environments.md:214
msgid ""
"If you're done trying out Nix for now, you may want to free up some disk "
"space occupied by the different versions of programs you downloaded by "
"running the examples:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/first-steps/ad-hoc-shell-environments.md:216
msgid "$ nix-collect-garbage\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/first-steps/ad-hoc-shell-environments.md:9
msgid ""
"Not all packages are supported for both Linux and macOS. Especially support "
"for graphical programs may vary."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/first-steps/ad-hoc-shell-environments.md:91
msgid ""
"A package name is not the same as a program name. Many packages provide "
"multiple programs, or no programs at all if they are libraries. Even for "
"packages that provide exactly one program, the package and program name are "
"not necessarily the same."
msgstr ""
